If you are a Lead, we process the following types of Personal Data about you:

biographical information, such as first and last name and date of birth; and contact information, such as email address, phone number, postal address, and country of residence postal;
employment information, such as industry, job title, company name, seniority within company, department name, or company size;
business contact information, such as company email address and postal address; and public LinkedIn profile;
analytics information, including the type of content that you engage with when using the Services, or after clicking a link in an outreach email;
device, internet and mobile information such as the hardware model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, browser type, language, IP address, wireless network, and mobile network information (including the mobile phone number);
geo-location information when you use the Services; and/or
records and copies of your correspondence (including e-mail addresses), if you contact us. This may include call recordings where we monitor and record such calls for staff training or quality assurance purposes.
If you are a Customer Representative, we process the following types of Personal Data about you:

business contact information such as first and last name, email address, phone number, postal address;
billing and payment information, including the address for billing, billing contact information and credit card information;
device, internet and mobile information such as the hardware model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, browser type, language, IP address, wireless network, and mobile network information (including the mobile phone number);
geo-location information when you use the Services; and/orrecords and copies of your correspondence (including e-mail addresses), if you contact us. This may include call recordings where we monitor and record such calls for staff training or quality assurance purposes.
If you are a Website Visitor, we process the following types of Personal Data about you:

contact information such as first and last name, email address and phone number;
device, internet and mobile information such as the hardware model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, browser type, language, IP address, wireless network, and mobile network information (including the mobile phone number);
geo-location information when you use our website; and/or
records and copies of your correspondence (including e-mail addresses), if you contact us. This may include call recordings where we monitor and record such calls for staff training or quality assurance purposes.

HOW WE RECEIVE PERSONAL DATA
If you are a Lead, we receive your Personal Data when:

you provide it directly to us through our Services, or by clicking a link in a Contentgine outreach email;
our Customers (including Customer Representatives) provide it to us;
we receive it from other companies within our corporate group;
our service providers provide it to us;
we obtain lists from our business partners and data vendors with respect to individuals who might be interested in becoming customers of or are otherwise interested in our Customers;
you provide it on publicly accessible sources, such as on LinkedIn or your company website; and/or
such information is captured via cookies and similar technologies (collectively referred to as “cookies”), as outlined in the “Cookie” section below.
If you are a Customer Representative, we receive your Personal Data when:

you provide it directly to us through our Services;
our Customers provide it to us; and/or
such information is captured via cookies and similar technologies (collectively referred to as “cookies”) as outlined in the “Cookie” section below.
If you are a Website Visitor, we receive your Personal Data when:

you provide it directly to us through our website; and/or
such information is captured via cookies and similar technologies (collectively referred to as “cookies”), as outlined in the “Cookie” section below.

PURPOSES OF PROCESSING
If you are a Lead, we process your Personal Data to:

respond to your requests or questions;
provide you with access to the Services and the content therein, including content that we send you on behalf of our Customers;
create a record for our Customers about your interactions, which we may enhance with additional information about you (e.g. your name, job title, location and email address); and/or

If you are a Customer Representative, we process your Personal Data to:

respond to your requests or questions;
process and complete transactions, including to obtain sales leads, and send you related information;
provide technical and other support to you;
send you promotional communications, such as providing you with information about services, features, surveys, newsletters, offers, and events; and providing other news or information about us, and the Lead Generation Services;
enable our service providers to perform certain responsibilities and provide certain services in connection with the Lead Generation Services and our business and operations;
provide you with notices about your account;
carry out our obligations and enforce our rights arising from any contracts entered into between you and us, including for billing and collection; and/or verify your identity and prevent fraud or other unauthorized or illegal activity.

